short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Display additional information through the community when searching on Google search engine.
short.fr: Affiche des informations supplémentaires grâce à la communauté lors de vos recherches sur le moteur de recherche Google.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
New: You can now divide the search result into 2 columns, if your account is configured to display 20 results and more (10 by default in Google Search)
Color cartridges are displayed before the results. The categories are :
WEBSITE
DOC
DEFINITION
FORUM
PROJECT
SERVICE
SOFT
COMPANY
NEWS
BLOG
SOCIAL
VIDEO
MUSIC
SHOP
DIRECTORY
